The paper discusses the representation and reasoning mechanisms in cognitive agents, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also introduces a novel categorization algorithm, which could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the theories of concepts, which could be categorized under cognitive science (cs.CC) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
